{
  "id": "adv_card_ktn_09_02",
  "title": "長瀬琴乃 2話 私が一人で繋ぎます",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――音楽フェス当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Music Festival Day",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gaya-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1333.333,
          "startTime": 1.333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festout-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festout-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_02-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "わぁ……人が沢山いますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow… There are so many people",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.1333333294,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "第一回からこれだけ動員出来るのは凄いな\n運営もよほど気合いを入れてるんだろう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's amazing to have so many people for the first event.\nThe management must be putting a lot of effort into it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.8333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2933.3333334000004,
          "startTime": 13.7666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festout-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festout-00-noon",
      "startTime": 13.6333333294
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_02-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "今日出演するアイドルは……あ！\nこのグループ、大好きなんですよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The idols performing today are… Ah!\nI really like this group!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_02-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "バンド系アイドルなんですけど、ドラムの子の\nパフォーマンスが凄くかっこ良くて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They're a band-style idol group‚ the drummer's\nperformance is really cool…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.3531077374,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festout-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festout-00-noon",
      "startTime": 26.3333333294
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そんなにはしゃぐとは、よっぽど好きなんだな\nこのグループの出番は十分後か。もうすぐだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You look so excited‚ you must really like them.\nThis group performs in 10 minutes. Almost time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.5290702145,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_02-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん……観に行ってもいいですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san… Can I go see them perform?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.2333333294,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festout-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festout-00-noon",
      "startTime": 40.3666666627
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "もちろんだ、行ってくるといい……と思ったけど\n琴乃に気付いたお客さんで大騒ぎになりそうだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course‚ go ahead and have fun…… I want to say that‚ but\nit seems to be a big commotion if the fans recognize you‚ Kotono.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.5269326866,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festout-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festout-00-noon",
      "startTime": 49.8666666627
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_02-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "それなら……帽子とマスクとサングラスを着けておけば\n大丈夫じゃないですか？　後はえっと、マフラーとか！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then…… if I put on a hat‚ a mask‚ and sunglasses‚\nwouldn't it be alright? And um‚ a muffler or something!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "夏のフェスでそんな姿をしてる人がいたら\nかえって注目されるだろ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If someone dressed like that at a summer festival‚\nthey'd get even more attention.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festout-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festout-00-noon",
      "startTime": 64.3666666627
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_02-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "確かに……この間、すずが不自然なくらい変装したら\n正体がバレた時以上に注目を集めてました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Certainly…… The other day‚ when Suzu wore an unnatural disguise‚\nshe got even more attention than when her identity was revealed.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festout-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festout-00-noon",
      "startTime": 74.0333333294
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "ダメだった事例があるんじゃないか……仕方ない\n俺もついて行くよ。いざとなったら盾になるから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You already know an example of it not working… Oh well‚\nI'll go with you. I'll be your shield if anything happens.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festout-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festout-00-noon",
      "startTime": 82.299999996
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_02-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "本当ですか！？　ありがとうございます！\nふふ……近くで観れるんだ。楽しみだなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really!? Thank you so much!\nFufu… I can see them up close. I'm excited~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.8741528559,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festin-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festin-00-noon",
      "startTime": 94.2166666627
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festin-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festin-00-noon",
      "startTime": 94.2166666627
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_02-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ～……とっても楽しいステージでした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haa… That was really fun.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.2666666627,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃がいるとバレなくて良かったよ。ただ……\nコール＆レスポンスで大声を出した時は焦ったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm glad they didn't find out you were there. But…\nI was startled when you shouted during the call and response.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festin-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festin-00-noon",
      "startTime": 109.799999996
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_02-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "う……す、すみません。あまりに楽しくてつい\n本番はこれからですし、気をつけます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… S-Sorry. I just got too excited\nThe actual broadcast starts now‚ so I'll be careful.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festin-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festin-00-noon",
      "startTime": 120.1666666627
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_02-ktn010.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば、雨が心配でしたけど……\n小降りで済んで良かったです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Come to think of it‚ I was worried about the rain‚ but…\nI'm glad it's just a drizzle.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.6,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_rain-02.m4a",
          "delay": 8066.666666700002,
          "startTime": 131.6666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "そうだな、ステージには一応屋根もあるし\n多少は吹き込むだろうけど、月ストも問題なく……ん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right‚ there's a roof on the stage anyway‚\nso even if some rain gets in‚ Moon Tempest will be fine… Hm?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festin-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festin-00-noon",
      "startTime": 134.7333333294
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_02-ktn011.m4a",
      "text": "雨……強くなって来ましたね。大丈夫でしょうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The rain… is getting stronger. Will we be okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.7333333294,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "ひとまず様子を見るしかないな\n天候が回復することを祈ろう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ for now‚ we can only wait and see.\nLet's hope the weather gets better.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.9333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_rain-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4099.994909799989,
          "startTime": 148.0333282431
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_fessmall-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "fessmall-01-evening",
      "startTime": 147.7333282471
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_fessmall-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "fessmall-01-evening",
      "startTime": 147.7333282471
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "まずいな……次が月ストの出番だっていうのに\nさらに雨足が……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is bad… The next performance is Moon Tempest's‚ but\nthe rain's getting even stronger…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.7666615804,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_02-ktn012.m4a",
      "text": "渚達は大丈夫でしょうか\nもう会場に着いてないといけない時間ですよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wonder if Nagisa and the others are okay.\nIt's already the time they should be arriving at the venue‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.4333282471,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-call-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6366.671752900003,
          "startTime": 163.8
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_fessmall-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "fessmall-01-evening",
      "startTime": 161.1333251913
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "そうだな。一度状況を確認して……ん？\n渚から電話だ。はい、もしもし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's true. Let me check the situation… Hm?\nIt's a call from Nagisa. Hello?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 165.699991862,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "え、雨で新幹線が遅れて今駅に到着した？\nしかも冠水の影響でタクシーの到着も遅れてるのか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What? the bullet train got delayed by the rain and you just arrived at the station?\nAnd the taxi is also delayed due to the flooding?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 173.6666605632,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_fessmall-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "fessmall-01-evening",
      "startTime": 178.0999938925
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_02-ktn013.m4a",
      "text": "私達の前のグループ、この曲がラストです\n入れ替えの時間を考えても後十五分くらいしか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The group before us is on their last song.\nEven with the set change‚ we only have about 15 minutes left…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 182.8999938965,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_fessmall-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "fessmall-01-evening",
      "startTime": 187.7666605592
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "どう考えても、渚達は開演時刻には\n間に合いそうにないな。どうする……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No matter how you look at it‚ Nagisa and the others\nwon't make it by the start time. What should I do……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 190.8669987228,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_02-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "（そもそも過密スケジュールでみんなただでさえ）\n（無理をしてるんだ。雨足もどんどん強くなってる）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（In the first place‚ everyone is already pushing themselves because of）\n（their tight schedules. The rain is getting stronger and stronger.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 198.1666605632,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_fessmall-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "fessmall-01-evening",
      "startTime": 202.2999938925
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_02-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "（こんな天候の中強行して、体調でも崩したら……）\n（そうなる前に、中止にした方が――）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（If we force them to perform in this weather and they end up getting sick…）\n（Before that happens‚ maybe it's better to cancel it--）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 206.7666605632,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_fessmall-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "fessmall-01-evening",
      "startTime": 209.4666605592
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
