      "text": "一人で？　いや、さすがにそんな無理はさせられない\n運営と交渉してみるから少し待ってくれないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alone? No‚ I can't make you do something that difficult.\nI'll try to negotiate with the management‚ so could you wait a little?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 226.4666605632,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_fessmall-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "fessmall-01-evening",
      "startTime": 229.7333272259
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
