      "text": "もう開演直前ですよ。今からタイムスケジュールの\n調整を入れるのは、無理があるんじゃないですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But the show is about to start. Changing the schedule\nnow would be impossible‚ don't you think?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 233.2260852754,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
