      "text": "私なら大丈夫です。月ストの曲を一人で歌っても\nいいですし、ソロ曲もあります",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll be fine. I can sing Moon Tempest's songs alone‚\nand I also have solo songs.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 240.9999938965,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
