      "text": "そこまで言うなら……分かった、琴乃に任せるよ\n渚。今、琴乃から――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you put it that way… Alright‚ I'll leave it to you‚ Kotono.\nNagisa. Just now‚ from Kotono--",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 264.9999938965,
      "sfxList": [
