      "text": "……さて。曲を決めて、スタッフと打ち合わせしないと\nいけないな。時間はないが……本当に大丈夫か？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "……Well then. We have to pick the songs and have a meeting\nwith the staff. There's no time… Are you really going to be okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
