      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_02-ktn020.m4a",
      "text": "はい。曲は{user}さんが\n通話してる間に決めましたから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. I decided on the song\nwhile {user}-san was on the phone.",
